        <section class="box special">
            <header class="major">
                <h2>Build together and be more productive!</h2>
                <p>Open up your data to others. Maintain control as to who edits. Review comments.<br/>
                    Engage a wider audience: researchers, teammates, native speakers. It's up to you.</p>
            </header>
            <!-- from: https://unsplash.com/photos/SYTO3xs06fU -->
